{"surah":{"number":54,"name":"القمر","englishName":"Al-Qamar","englishTranslation":"The Moon","ayahCount":55},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:17.187Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"The Hour has come near, and the moon has split [in two].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱقْتَرَبَتِ","english":"Has come near","translit":"iq'tarabati","root":"قرب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلسَّاعَةُ","english":"the Hour","translit":"l-sāʿatu","root":"سوع"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَٱنشَقَّ","english":"and has split","translit":"wa-inshaqqa","root":"شقق"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْقَمَرُ","english":"the moon","translit":"l-qamaru","root":"قمر"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"And if they see a miracle, they turn away and say, \"Passing magic.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِن","english":"And if","translit":"wa-in","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَرَوْا۟","english":"they see","translit":"yaraw","root":"رأي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ءَايَةًۭ","english":"a Sign","translit":"āyatan","root":"أيي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"يُعْرِضُوا۟","english":"they turn away","translit":"yuʿ'riḍū","root":"عرض"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَيَقُولُوا۟","english":"and say","translit":"wayaqūlū","root":"قول"},{"position":6,"arabic":"سِحْرٌۭ","english":"Magic","translit":"siḥ'run","root":"سحر"},{"position":7,"arabic":"مُّسْتَمِرٌّۭ","english":"continuing","translit":"mus'tamirrun","root":"مرر"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"And they denied and followed their inclinations. But for every matter is a [time of] settlement.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَكَذَّبُوا۟","english":"And they denied","translit":"wakadhabū","root":"كذب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَٱتَّبَعُوٓا۟","english":"and followed","translit":"wa-ittabaʿū","root":"تبع"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَهْوَآءَهُمْ ۚ","english":"their desires","translit":"ahwāahum","root":"هوي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَكُلُّ","english":"but (for) every","translit":"wakullu","root":"كلل","audio":"wbw/054_003_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَمْرٍۢ","english":"matter","translit":"amrin","root":"أمر","audio":"wbw/054_003_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مُّسْتَقِرٌّۭ","english":"(will be a) settlement","translit":"mus'taqirrun","root":"قرر","audio":"wbw/054_003_007.mp3"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"And there has already come to them of information that in which there is deterrence -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","english":"And certainly","translit":"walaqad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"جَآءَهُم","english":"has come to them","translit":"jāahum","root":"جيأ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِّنَ","english":"of","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْأَنۢبَآءِ","english":"the information","translit":"l-anbāi","root":"نبأ"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مَا","english":"wherein","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"فِيهِ","english":"wherein","translit":"fīhi","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"مُزْدَجَرٌ","english":"(is) deterrence","translit":"muz'dajarun","root":"زجر"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"Extensive wisdom - but warning does not avail [them].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"حِكْمَةٌۢ","english":"Wisdom","translit":"ḥik'matun","root":"حكم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بَـٰلِغَةٌۭ ۖ","english":"perfect","translit":"bālighatun","root":"بلغ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَمَا","english":"but not","translit":"famā","root":"","audio":"wbw/054_005_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُغْنِ","english":"will avail","translit":"tugh'ni","root":"غني","audio":"wbw/054_005_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلنُّذُرُ","english":"the warnings","translit":"l-nudhuru","root":"نذر","audio":"wbw/054_005_006.mp3"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"So leave them, [O Muhammad]. The Day the Caller calls to something forbidding,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَتَوَلَّ","english":"So turn away","translit":"fatawalla","root":"ولي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَنْهُمْ ۘ","english":"from them","translit":"ʿanhum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(The) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم","audio":"wbw/054_006_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"يَدْعُ","english":"will call","translit":"yadʿu","root":"دعو","audio":"wbw/054_006_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلدَّاعِ","english":"the caller","translit":"l-dāʿi","root":"دعو","audio":"wbw/054_006_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":"","audio":"wbw/054_006_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"شَىْءٍۢ","english":"a thing","translit":"shayin","root":"شيأ","audio":"wbw/054_006_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"نُّكُرٍ","english":"terrible","translit":"nukurin","root":"نكر","audio":"wbw/054_006_009.mp3"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"Their eyes humbled, they will emerge from the graves as if they were locusts spreading,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"خُشَّعًا","english":"(Will be) humbled","translit":"khushaʿan","root":"خشع"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَبْصَـٰرُهُمْ","english":"their eyes","translit":"abṣāruhum","root":"بصر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"يَخْرُجُونَ","english":"they will come forth","translit":"yakhrujūna","root":"خرج"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِنَ","english":"from","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْأَجْدَاثِ","english":"the graves","translit":"l-ajdāthi","root":"جدث"},{"position":6,"arabic":"كَأَنَّهُمْ","english":"as if they (were)","translit":"ka-annahum","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"جَرَادٌۭ","english":"locusts","translit":"jarādun","root":"جرد"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مُّنتَشِرٌۭ","english":"spreading","translit":"muntashirun","root":"نشر"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"Racing ahead toward the Caller. The disbelievers will say, \"This is a difficult Day.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مُّهْطِعِينَ","english":"Racing ahead","translit":"muh'ṭiʿīna","root":"هطع"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِلَى","english":"towards","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلدَّاعِ ۖ","english":"the caller","translit":"l-dāʿi","root":"دعو"},{"position":4,"arabic":"يَقُولُ","english":"Will say","translit":"yaqūlu","root":"قول","audio":"wbw/054_008_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْكَـٰفِرُونَ","english":"the disbelievers","translit":"l-kāfirūna","root":"كفر","audio":"wbw/054_008_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"هَـٰذَا","english":"This","translit":"hādhā","root":"","audio":"wbw/054_008_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"يَوْمٌ","english":"(is) a Day","translit":"yawmun","root":"يوم","audio":"wbw/054_008_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"عَسِرٌۭ","english":"difficult","translit":"ʿasirun","root":"عسر","audio":"wbw/054_008_009.mp3"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"The people of Noah denied before them, and they denied Our servant and said, \"A madman,\" and he was repelled.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"۞ كَذَّبَتْ","english":"Denied","translit":"kadhabat","root":"كذب","audio":"wbw/054_009_002.mp3"},{"position":2,"arabic":"قَبْلَهُمْ","english":"before them","translit":"qablahum","root":"قبل","audio":"wbw/054_009_003.mp3"},{"position":3,"arabic":"قَوْمُ","english":"(the) people","translit":"qawmu","root":"قوم","audio":"wbw/054_009_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"نُوحٍۢ","english":"(of) Nuh","translit":"nūḥin","root":"","audio":"wbw/054_009_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"فَكَذَّبُوا۟","english":"and they denied","translit":"fakadhabū","root":"كذب","audio":"wbw/054_009_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"عَبْدَنَا","english":"Our slave","translit":"ʿabdanā","root":"عبد","audio":"wbw/054_009_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَقَالُوا۟","english":"and said","translit":"waqālū","root":"قول","audio":"wbw/054_009_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مَجْنُونٌۭ","english":"A madman","translit":"majnūnun","root":"جنن","audio":"wbw/054_009_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَٱزْدُجِرَ","english":"and he was repelled","translit":"wa-uz'dujira","root":"زجر","audio":"wbw/054_009_010.mp3"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"So he invoked his Lord, \"Indeed, I am overpowered, so help.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَدَعَا","english":"So he called","translit":"fadaʿā","root":"دعو"},{"position":2,"arabic":"رَبَّهُۥٓ","english":"his Lord","translit":"rabbahu","root":"ربب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَنِّى","english":"I am","translit":"annī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَغْلُوبٌۭ","english":"one overpowered","translit":"maghlūbun","root":"غلب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"فَٱنتَصِرْ","english":"so help","translit":"fa-intaṣir","root":"نصر"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"Then We opened the gates of the heaven with rain pouring down","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَفَتَحْنَآ","english":"So We opened","translit":"fafataḥnā","root":"فتح"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَبْوَٰبَ","english":"(the) gates","translit":"abwāba","root":"بوب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَآءِ","english":"(of) heaven","translit":"l-samāi","root":"سمو"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بِمَآءٍۢ","english":"with water","translit":"bimāin","root":"موه"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مُّنْهَمِرٍۢ","english":"pouring down","translit":"mun'hamirin","root":"همر"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"And caused the earth to burst with springs, and the waters met for a matter already predestined.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَفَجَّرْنَا","english":"And We caused to burst","translit":"wafajjarnā","root":"فجر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضَ","english":"the earth","translit":"l-arḍa","root":"أرض"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عُيُونًۭا","english":"(with) springs","translit":"ʿuyūnan","root":"عين"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَٱلْتَقَى","english":"so met","translit":"fal-taqā","root":"لقي"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْمَآءُ","english":"the water(s)","translit":"l-māu","root":"موه"},{"position":6,"arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ","english":"for","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"أَمْرٍۢ","english":"a matter","translit":"amrin","root":"أمر"},{"position":8,"arabic":"قَدْ","english":"already","translit":"qad","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"قُدِرَ","english":"predestined","translit":"qudira","root":"قدر"}]},{"number":13,"translation":"And We carried him on a [construction of] planks and nails,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَحَمَلْنَـٰهُ","english":"And We carried him","translit":"waḥamalnāhu","root":"حمل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"on","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ذَاتِ","english":"(ark) made of planks","translit":"dhāti","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَلْوَٰحٍۢ","english":"(ark) made of planks","translit":"alwāḥin","root":"لوح"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَدُسُرٍۢ","english":"and nails","translit":"wadusurin","root":"دسر"}]},{"number":14,"translation":"Sailing under Our observation as reward for he who had been denied.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"تَجْرِى","english":"Sailing","translit":"tajrī","root":"جري"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بِأَعْيُنِنَا","english":"before Our eyes","translit":"bi-aʿyuninā","root":"عين"},{"position":3,"arabic":"جَزَآءًۭ","english":"a reward","translit":"jazāan","root":"جزي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لِّمَن","english":"for (he) who","translit":"liman","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"was","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":6,"arabic":"كُفِرَ","english":"denied","translit":"kufira","root":"كفر"}]},{"number":15,"translation":"And We left it as a sign, so is there any who will remember?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَد","english":"And certainly","translit":"walaqad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تَّرَكْنَـٰهَآ","english":"We left it","translit":"taraknāhā","root":"ترك"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ءَايَةًۭ","english":"(as) a Sign","translit":"āyatan","root":"أيي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَهَلْ","english":"so is (there)","translit":"fahal","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِن","english":"any","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"مُّدَّكِرٍۢ","english":"who will receive admonition","translit":"muddakirin","root":"ذكر"}]},{"number":16,"translation":"And how [severe] were My punishment and warning.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَكَيْفَ","english":"So how","translit":"fakayfa","root":"كيف"},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"was","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَذَابِى","english":"My punishment","translit":"ʿadhābī","root":"عذب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَنُذُرِ","english":"and My warnings","translit":"wanudhuri","root":"نذر"}]},{"number":17,"translation":"And We have certainly made the Qur'an easy for remembrance, so is there any who will remember?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","english":"And certainly","translit":"walaqad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَسَّرْنَا","english":"We have made easy","translit":"yassarnā","root":"يسر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْقُرْءَانَ","english":"the Quran","translit":"l-qur'āna","root":"قرأ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لِلذِّكْرِ","english":"for remembrance","translit":"lildhik'ri","root":"ذكر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"فَهَلْ","english":"so is (there)","translit":"fahal","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"مِن","english":"any","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"مُّدَّكِرٍۢ","english":"who will receive admonition","translit":"muddakirin","root":"ذكر"}]},{"number":18,"translation":"'Aad denied; and how [severe] were My punishment and warning.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَذَّبَتْ","english":"Denied","translit":"kadhabat","root":"كذب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَادٌۭ","english":"Aad","translit":"ʿādun","root":"عود"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَكَيْفَ","english":"so how","translit":"fakayfa","root":"كيف"},{"position":4,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"was","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":5,"arabic":"عَذَابِى","english":"My punishment","translit":"ʿadhābī","root":"عذب"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَنُذُرِ","english":"and My warnings","translit":"wanudhuri","root":"نذر"}]},{"number":19,"translation":"Indeed, We sent upon them a screaming wind on a day of continuous misfortune,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّآ","english":"Indeed, We","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَرْسَلْنَا","english":"[We] sent","translit":"arsalnā","root":"رسل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمْ","english":"upon them","translit":"ʿalayhim","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"رِيحًۭا","english":"a wind","translit":"rīḥan","root":"روح"},{"position":5,"arabic":"صَرْصَرًۭا","english":"furious","translit":"ṣarṣaran","root":"صرصر"},{"position":6,"arabic":"فِى","english":"on","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"يَوْمِ","english":"a day","translit":"yawmi","root":"يوم"},{"position":8,"arabic":"نَحْسٍۢ","english":"(of) misfortune","translit":"naḥsin","root":"نحس"},{"position":9,"arabic":"مُّسْتَمِرٍّۢ","english":"continuous","translit":"mus'tamirrin","root":"مرر"}]},{"number":20,"translation":"Extracting the people as if they were trunks of palm trees uprooted.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"تَنزِعُ","english":"Plucking out","translit":"tanziʿu","root":"نزع"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاسَ","english":"men","translit":"l-nāsa","root":"أنس"},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَأَنَّهُمْ","english":"as if they (were)","translit":"ka-annahum","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَعْجَازُ","english":"trunks","translit":"aʿjāzu","root":"عجز"},{"position":5,"arabic":"نَخْلٍۢ","english":"(of) date-palms","translit":"nakhlin","root":"نخل"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مُّنقَعِرٍۢ","english":"uprooted","translit":"munqaʿirin","root":"قعر"}]},{"number":21,"translation":"And how [severe] were My punishment and warning.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَكَيْفَ","english":"So how","translit":"fakayfa","root":"كيف"},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"was","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَذَابِى","english":"My punishment","translit":"ʿadhābī","root":"عذب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَنُذُرِ","english":"and My warnings","translit":"wanudhuri","root":"نذر"}]},{"number":22,"translation":"And We have certainly made the Qur'an easy for remembrance, so is there any who will remember?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","english":"And certainly","translit":"walaqad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَسَّرْنَا","english":"We have made easy","translit":"yassarnā","root":"يسر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْقُرْءَانَ","english":"the Quran","translit":"l-qur'āna","root":"قرأ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لِلذِّكْرِ","english":"for remembrance","translit":"lildhik'ri","root":"ذكر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"فَهَلْ","english":"so is (there)","translit":"fahal","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"مِن","english":"any","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"مُّدَّكِرٍۢ","english":"who will receive admonition","translit":"muddakirin","root":"ذكر"}]},{"number":23,"translation":"Thamud denied the warning","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَذَّبَتْ","english":"Denied","translit":"kadhabat","root":"كذب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ثَمُودُ","english":"Thamud","translit":"thamūdu","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِٱلنُّذُرِ","english":"the warnings","translit":"bil-nudhuri","root":"نذر"}]},{"number":24,"translation":"And said, \"Is it one human being among us that we should follow? Indeed, we would then be in error and madness.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَقَالُوٓا۟","english":"And said","translit":"faqālū","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَبَشَرًۭا","english":"Is (it) a human being","translit":"abasharan","root":"بشر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِّنَّا","english":"among us","translit":"minnā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَٰحِدًۭا","english":"one","translit":"wāḥidan","root":"وحد"},{"position":5,"arabic":"نَّتَّبِعُهُۥٓ","english":"(that) we should follow him","translit":"nattabiʿuhu","root":"تبع"},{"position":6,"arabic":"إِنَّآ","english":"Indeed, we","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"إِذًۭا","english":"then","translit":"idhan","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"لَّفِى","english":"(will be) surely in","translit":"lafī","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"ضَلَـٰلٍۢ","english":"error","translit":"ḍalālin","root":"ضلل"},{"position":10,"arabic":"وَسُعُرٍ","english":"and madness","translit":"wasuʿurin","root":"سعر"}]},{"number":25,"translation":"Has the message been sent down upon him from among us? Rather, he is an insolent liar.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَءُلْقِىَ","english":"Has been sent","translit":"a-ul'qiya","root":"لقي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلذِّكْرُ","english":"the Reminder","translit":"l-dhik'ru","root":"ذكر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","english":"to him","translit":"ʿalayhi","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِنۢ","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"بَيْنِنَا","english":"among us","translit":"bayninā","root":"بين"},{"position":6,"arabic":"بَلْ","english":"Nay","translit":"bal","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"هُوَ","english":"he","translit":"huwa","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"كَذَّابٌ","english":"(is) a liar","translit":"kadhābun","root":"كذب"},{"position":9,"arabic":"أَشِرٌۭ","english":"insolent","translit":"ashirun","root":"أشر"}]},{"number":26,"translation":"They will know tomorrow who is the insolent liar.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"سَيَعْلَمُونَ","english":"They will know","translit":"sayaʿlamūna","root":"علم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"غَدًۭا","english":"tomorrow","translit":"ghadan","root":"غدو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَّنِ","english":"who","translit":"mani","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْكَذَّابُ","english":"(is) the liar","translit":"l-kadhābu","root":"كذب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْأَشِرُ","english":"the insolent one","translit":"l-ashiru","root":"أشر"}]},{"number":27,"translation":"Indeed, We are sending the she-camel as trial for them, so watch them and be patient.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّا","english":"Indeed, We","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مُرْسِلُوا۟","english":"(are) sending","translit":"mur'silū","root":"رسل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاقَةِ","english":"the she-camel","translit":"l-nāqati","root":"نوق"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فِتْنَةًۭ","english":"(as) a trial","translit":"fit'natan","root":"فتن"},{"position":5,"arabic":"لَّهُمْ","english":"for them","translit":"lahum","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"فَٱرْتَقِبْهُمْ","english":"so watch them","translit":"fa-ir'taqib'hum","root":"رقب"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَٱصْطَبِرْ","english":"and be patient","translit":"wa-iṣ'ṭabir","root":"صبر"}]},{"number":28,"translation":"And inform them that the water is shared between them, each [day of] drink attended [by turn].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَنَبِّئْهُمْ","english":"And inform them","translit":"wanabbi'hum","root":"نبأ"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَنَّ","english":"that","translit":"anna","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْمَآءَ","english":"the water","translit":"l-māa","root":"موه"},{"position":4,"arabic":"قِسْمَةٌۢ","english":"(is) to be shared","translit":"qis'matun","root":"قسم"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بَيْنَهُمْ ۖ","english":"between them","translit":"baynahum","root":"بين"},{"position":6,"arabic":"كُلُّ","english":"each","translit":"kullu","root":"كلل","audio":"wbw/054_028_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"شِرْبٍۢ","english":"drink","translit":"shir'bin","root":"شرب","audio":"wbw/054_028_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مُّحْتَضَرٌۭ","english":"attended","translit":"muḥ'taḍarun","root":"حضر","audio":"wbw/054_028_009.mp3"}]},{"number":29,"translation":"But they called their companion, and he dared and hamstrung [her].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَنَادَوْا۟","english":"But they called","translit":"fanādaw","root":"ندي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"صَاحِبَهُمْ","english":"their companion","translit":"ṣāḥibahum","root":"صحب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَتَعَاطَىٰ","english":"and he took","translit":"fataʿāṭā","root":"عطو"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَعَقَرَ","english":"and hamstrung","translit":"faʿaqara","root":"عقر"}]},{"number":30,"translation":"And how [severe] were My punishment and warning.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَكَيْفَ","english":"So how","translit":"fakayfa","root":"كيف"},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"was","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَذَابِى","english":"My punishment","translit":"ʿadhābī","root":"عذب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَنُذُرِ","english":"and My warnings","translit":"wanudhuri","root":"نذر"}]},{"number":31,"translation":"Indeed, We sent upon them one blast from the sky, and they became like the dry twig fragments of an [animal] pen.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّآ","english":"Indeed, We","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَرْسَلْنَا","english":"[We] sent","translit":"arsalnā","root":"رسل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمْ","english":"upon them","translit":"ʿalayhim","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"صَيْحَةًۭ","english":"thunderous blast","translit":"ṣayḥatan","root":"صيح"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَٰحِدَةًۭ","english":"single","translit":"wāḥidatan","root":"وحد"},{"position":6,"arabic":"فَكَانُوا۟","english":"and they became","translit":"fakānū","root":"كون"},{"position":7,"arabic":"كَهَشِيمِ","english":"like dry twig fragments","translit":"kahashīmi","root":"هشم"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْمُحْتَظِرِ","english":"(used by) a fence builder","translit":"l-muḥ'taẓiri","root":"حظر"}]},{"number":32,"translation":"And We have certainly made the Qur'an easy for remembrance, so is there any who will remember?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","english":"And certainly","translit":"walaqad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَسَّرْنَا","english":"We have made easy","translit":"yassarnā","root":"يسر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْقُرْءَانَ","english":"the Quran","translit":"l-qur'āna","root":"قرأ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لِلذِّكْرِ","english":"for remembrance","translit":"lildhik'ri","root":"ذكر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"فَهَلْ","english":"so is (there)","translit":"fahal","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"مِن","english":"any","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"مُّدَّكِرٍۢ","english":"who will receive admonition","translit":"muddakirin","root":"ذكر"}]},{"number":33,"translation":"The people of Lot denied the warning.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَذَّبَتْ","english":"Denied","translit":"kadhabat","root":"كذب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"قَوْمُ","english":"(the) people","translit":"qawmu","root":"قوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لُوطٍۭ","english":"(of) Lut","translit":"lūṭin","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"بِٱلنُّذُرِ","english":"the warnings","translit":"bil-nudhuri","root":"نذر"}]},{"number":34,"translation":"Indeed, We sent upon them a storm of stones, except the family of Lot - We saved them before dawn","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّآ","english":"Indeed, We","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَرْسَلْنَا","english":"[We] sent","translit":"arsalnā","root":"رسل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمْ","english":"upon them","translit":"ʿalayhim","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"حَاصِبًا","english":"a storm of stones","translit":"ḥāṣiban","root":"حصب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"إِلَّآ","english":"except","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"ءَالَ","english":"(the) family","translit":"āla","root":"أول"},{"position":7,"arabic":"لُوطٍۢ ۖ","english":"(of) Lut","translit":"lūṭin","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"نَّجَّيْنَـٰهُم","english":"We saved them","translit":"najjaynāhum","root":"نجو","audio":"wbw/054_034_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"بِسَحَرٍۢ","english":"by dawn","translit":"bisaḥarin","root":"سحر","audio":"wbw/054_034_010.mp3"}]},{"number":35,"translation":"As favor from us. Thus do We reward he who is grateful.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"نِّعْمَةًۭ","english":"(As) a favor","translit":"niʿ'matan","root":"نعم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِّنْ","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"عِندِنَا ۚ","english":"Us","translit":"ʿindinā","root":"عند"},{"position":4,"arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ","english":"Thus","translit":"kadhālika","root":"","audio":"wbw/054_035_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"نَجْزِى","english":"We reward","translit":"najzī","root":"جزي","audio":"wbw/054_035_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مَن","english":"(one) who","translit":"man","root":"","audio":"wbw/054_035_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"شَكَرَ","english":"(is) grateful","translit":"shakara","root":"شكر","audio":"wbw/054_035_008.mp3"}]},{"number":36,"translation":"And he had already warned them of Our assault, but they disputed the warning.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","english":"And certainly","translit":"walaqad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَنذَرَهُم","english":"he warned them","translit":"andharahum","root":"نذر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بَطْشَتَنَا","english":"(of) Our seizure","translit":"baṭshatanā","root":"بطش"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَتَمَارَوْا۟","english":"but they disputed","translit":"fatamāraw","root":"مري"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِٱلنُّذُرِ","english":"the warnings","translit":"bil-nudhuri","root":"نذر"}]},{"number":37,"translation":"And they had demanded from him his guests, but We obliterated their eyes, [saying], \"Taste My punishment and warning.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","english":"And certainly","translit":"walaqad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"رَٰوَدُوهُ","english":"they demanded from him","translit":"rāwadūhu","root":"رود"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَن","english":"they demanded from him","translit":"ʿan","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ضَيْفِهِۦ","english":"his guests","translit":"ḍayfihi","root":"ضيف"},{"position":5,"arabic":"فَطَمَسْنَآ","english":"so We blinded","translit":"faṭamasnā","root":"طمس"},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَعْيُنَهُمْ","english":"their eyes","translit":"aʿyunahum","root":"عين"},{"position":7,"arabic":"فَذُوقُوا۟","english":"So taste","translit":"fadhūqū","root":"ذوق"},{"position":8,"arabic":"عَذَابِى","english":"My punishment","translit":"ʿadhābī","root":"عذب"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَنُذُرِ","english":"and My warnings","translit":"wanudhuri","root":"نذر"}]},{"number":38,"translation":"And there came upon them by morning an abiding punishment.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","english":"And certainly","translit":"walaqad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"صَبَّحَهُم","english":"seized them in the morning","translit":"ṣabbaḥahum","root":"صبح"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بُكْرَةً","english":"early","translit":"buk'ratan","root":"بكر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"عَذَابٌۭ","english":"a punishment","translit":"ʿadhābun","root":"عذب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مُّسْتَقِرٌّۭ","english":"abiding","translit":"mus'taqirrun","root":"قرر"}]},{"number":39,"translation":"So taste My punishment and warning.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَذُوقُوا۟","english":"So taste","translit":"fadhūqū","root":"ذوق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَذَابِى","english":"My punishment","translit":"ʿadhābī","root":"عذب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَنُذُرِ","english":"and My warnings","translit":"wanudhuri","root":"نذر"}]},{"number":40,"translation":"And We have certainly made the Qur'an easy for remembrance, so is there any who will remember?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","english":"And certainly","translit":"walaqad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَسَّرْنَا","english":"We have made easy","translit":"yassarnā","root":"يسر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْقُرْءَانَ","english":"the Quran","translit":"l-qur'āna","root":"قرأ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لِلذِّكْرِ","english":"for remembrance","translit":"lildhik'ri","root":"ذكر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"فَهَلْ","english":"so is (there)","translit":"fahal","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"مِن","english":"any","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"مُّدَّكِرٍۢ","english":"who will receive admonition","translit":"muddakirin","root":"ذكر"}]},{"number":41,"translation":"And there certainly came to the people of Pharaoh warning.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","english":"And certainly","translit":"walaqad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"جَآءَ","english":"came","translit":"jāa","root":"جيأ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ءَالَ","english":"(to the) people","translit":"āla","root":"أول"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فِرْعَوْنَ","english":"(of) Firaun","translit":"fir'ʿawna","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلنُّذُرُ","english":"warnings","translit":"l-nudhuru","root":"نذر"}]},{"number":42,"translation":"They denied Our signs, all of them, so We seized them with a seizure of one Exalted in Might and Perfect in Ability.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَذَّبُوا۟","english":"They denied","translit":"kadhabū","root":"كذب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بِـَٔايَـٰتِنَا","english":"Our Signs","translit":"biāyātinā","root":"أيي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"كُلِّهَا","english":"all of them","translit":"kullihā","root":"كلل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَأَخَذْنَـٰهُمْ","english":"so We seized them","translit":"fa-akhadhnāhum","root":"أخذ"},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَخْذَ","english":"(with) a seizure","translit":"akhdha","root":"أخذ"},{"position":6,"arabic":"عَزِيزٍۢ","english":"(of) All-Mighty","translit":"ʿazīzin","root":"عزز"},{"position":7,"arabic":"مُّقْتَدِرٍ","english":"(the) Powerful One","translit":"muq'tadirin","root":"قدر"}]},{"number":43,"translation":"Are your disbelievers better than those [former ones], or have you immunity in the scripture?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَكُفَّارُكُمْ","english":"Are your disbelievers","translit":"akuffārukum","root":"كفر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"خَيْرٌۭ","english":"better","translit":"khayrun","root":"خير"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِّنْ","english":"than","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"أُو۟لَـٰٓئِكُمْ","english":"those","translit":"ulāikum","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَمْ","english":"or","translit":"am","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"لَكُم","english":"for you","translit":"lakum","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"بَرَآءَةٌۭ","english":"(is) an exemption","translit":"barāatun","root":"برأ"},{"position":8,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلزُّبُرِ","english":"the Scriptures","translit":"l-zuburi","root":"زبر"}]},{"number":44,"translation":"Or do they say, \"We are an assembly supporting [each other]\"?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَمْ","english":"Or","translit":"am","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَقُولُونَ","english":"(do) they say","translit":"yaqūlūna","root":"قول"},{"position":3,"arabic":"نَحْنُ","english":"We","translit":"naḥnu","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"جَمِيعٌۭ","english":"(are) an assembly","translit":"jamīʿun","root":"جمع"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مُّنتَصِرٌۭ","english":"helping (each other)","translit":"muntaṣirun","root":"نصر"}]},{"number":45,"translation":"[Their] assembly will be defeated, and they will turn their backs [in retreat].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"سَيُهْزَمُ","english":"Soon will be defeated","translit":"sayuh'zamu","root":"هزم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْجَمْعُ","english":"(their) assembly","translit":"l-jamʿu","root":"جمع"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَيُوَلُّونَ","english":"and they will turn","translit":"wayuwallūna","root":"ولي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلدُّبُرَ","english":"(their) backs","translit":"l-dubura","root":"دبر"}]},{"number":46,"translation":"But the Hour is their appointment [for due punishment], and the Hour is more disastrous and more bitter.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"بَلِ","english":"Nay","translit":"bali","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلسَّاعَةُ","english":"the Hour","translit":"l-sāʿatu","root":"سوع"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَوْعِدُهُمْ","english":"(is) their promised time","translit":"mawʿiduhum","root":"وعد"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَٱلسَّاعَةُ","english":"and the Hour","translit":"wal-sāʿatu","root":"سوع"},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَدْهَىٰ","english":"(will be) more grievous","translit":"adhā","root":"دهي"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَأَمَرُّ","english":"and more bitter","translit":"wa-amarru","root":"مرر"}]},{"number":47,"translation":"Indeed, the criminals are in error and madness.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْمُجْرِمِينَ","english":"the criminals","translit":"l-muj'rimīna","root":"جرم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","english":"(are) in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ضَلَـٰلٍۢ","english":"an error","translit":"ḍalālin","root":"ضلل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَسُعُرٍۢ","english":"and madness","translit":"wasuʿurin","root":"سعر"}]},{"number":48,"translation":"The Day they are dragged into the Fire on their faces [it will be said], \"Taste the touch of Saqar.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(The) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يُسْحَبُونَ","english":"they will be dragged","translit":"yus'ḥabūna","root":"سحب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","english":"into","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلنَّارِ","english":"the Fire","translit":"l-nāri","root":"نور"},{"position":5,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"on","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"وُجُوهِهِمْ","english":"their faces","translit":"wujūhihim","root":"وجه"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ذُوقُوا۟","english":"Taste","translit":"dhūqū","root":"ذوق"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مَسَّ","english":"(the) touch","translit":"massa","root":"مسس"},{"position":9,"arabic":"سَقَرَ","english":"(of) Hell","translit":"saqara","root":""}]},{"number":49,"translation":"Indeed, all things We created with predestination.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّا","english":"Indeed, [We]","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"كُلَّ","english":"every","translit":"kulla","root":"كلل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"شَىْءٍ","english":"thing","translit":"shayin","root":"شيأ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"خَلَقْنَـٰهُ","english":"We created it","translit":"khalaqnāhu","root":"خلق"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِقَدَرٍۢ","english":"by a measure","translit":"biqadarin","root":"قدر"}]},{"number":50,"translation":"And Our command is but one, like a glance of the eye.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَآ","english":"And not","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَمْرُنَآ","english":"(is) Our Command","translit":"amrunā","root":"أمر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"but","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَٰحِدَةٌۭ","english":"one","translit":"wāḥidatun","root":"وحد"},{"position":5,"arabic":"كَلَمْحٍۭ","english":"like the twinkling","translit":"kalamḥin","root":"لمح"},{"position":6,"arabic":"بِٱلْبَصَرِ","english":"(of) the eye","translit":"bil-baṣari","root":"بصر"}]},{"number":51,"translation":"And We have already destroyed your kinds, so is there any who will remember?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","english":"And certainly","translit":"walaqad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَهْلَكْنَآ","english":"We destroyed","translit":"ahlaknā","root":"هلك"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَشْيَاعَكُمْ","english":"your kinds","translit":"ashyāʿakum","root":"شيع"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَهَلْ","english":"so is (there)","translit":"fahal","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِن","english":"any","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"مُّدَّكِرٍۢ","english":"who will receive admonition","translit":"muddakirin","root":"ذكر"}]},{"number":52,"translation":"And everything they did is in written records.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَكُلُّ","english":"And every","translit":"wakullu","root":"كلل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"شَىْءٍۢ","english":"thing","translit":"shayin","root":"شيأ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَعَلُوهُ","english":"they did","translit":"faʿalūhu","root":"فعل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فِى","english":"(is) in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلزُّبُرِ","english":"the written records","translit":"l-zuburi","root":"زبر"}]},{"number":53,"translation":"And every small and great [thing] is inscribed.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَكُلُّ","english":"And every","translit":"wakullu","root":"كلل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"صَغِيرٍۢ","english":"small","translit":"ṣaghīrin","root":"صغر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَكَبِيرٍۢ","english":"and big","translit":"wakabīrin","root":"كبر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مُّسْتَطَرٌ","english":"(is) written down","translit":"mus'taṭarun","root":"سطر"}]},{"number":54,"translation":"Indeed, the righteous will be among gardens and rivers,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْمُتَّقِينَ","english":"the righteous","translit":"l-mutaqīna","root":"وقي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","english":"(will be) in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"جَنَّـٰتٍۢ","english":"gardens","translit":"jannātin","root":"جنن"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَنَهَرٍۢ","english":"and river","translit":"wanaharin","root":"نهر"}]},{"number":55,"translation":"In a seat of honor near a Sovereign, Perfect in Ability.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فِى","english":"In","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَقْعَدِ","english":"a seat","translit":"maqʿadi","root":"قعد"},{"position":3,"arabic":"صِدْقٍ","english":"(of) honor","translit":"ṣid'qin","root":"صدق"},{"position":4,"arabic":"عِندَ","english":"near","translit":"ʿinda","root":"عند"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مَلِيكٍۢ","english":"a King","translit":"malīkin","root":"ملك"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مُّقْتَدِرٍۭ","english":"Most Powerful","translit":"muq'tadirin","root":"قدر"}]}]}
